>>SOURCE FORMAT FREE
*> 30INTNE0 — documents: file access for the DOCINTNT indexed file
*> (document_intent, one row per document, replaced on reprocess).
*> Ops: GET · WRT · DEL. L-RET: 00 · 23 · 22 · 9x.
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. "30INTNE0".
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
FILE-CONTROL.
    SELECT INTN-FILE ASSIGN TO "DOCINTNT"
        ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
        ACCESS MODE IS DYNAMIC
        RECORD KEY IS DI-DOC
        LOCK MODE IS AUTOMATIC
        FILE STATUS IS WS-FS.
DATA DIVISION.
FILE SECTION.
FD INTN-FILE.
COPY "30INTNR0.cpy" REPLACING ==:PFX:== BY ==DI==.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-FS                PIC X(2).
LINKAGE SECTION.
01 L-OP                 PIC X(4).
01 L-RET                PIC X(2).
COPY "30INTNR0.cpy" REPLACING ==:PFX:== BY ==L-DI==.
PROCEDURE DIVISION USING L-OP L-RET L-DI-REC.
MAIN.
    PERFORM OPEN-FILE
    IF L-RET NOT = "00"
        GOBACK
    END-IF
    EVALUATE L-OP
        WHEN "GET " PERFORM DO-GET
        WHEN "WRT " PERFORM DO-WRITE
        WHEN "DEL " PERFORM DO-DELETE
        WHEN OTHER  MOVE "99" TO L-RET
    END-EVALUATE
    CLOSE INTN-FILE
    GOBACK.

OPEN-FILE.
    MOVE "00" TO L-RET
    OPEN I-O INTN-FILE
    IF WS-FS = "35"
        OPEN OUTPUT INTN-FILE
        CLOSE INTN-FILE
        OPEN I-O INTN-FILE
    END-IF
    IF WS-FS NOT = "00" AND WS-FS NOT = "05"
        MOVE "91" TO L-RET
    END-IF.

DO-GET.
    MOVE L-DI-DOC TO DI-DOC
    READ INTN-FILE
    IF WS-FS = "00" OR WS-FS = "02"
        MOVE DI-REC TO L-DI-REC
        MOVE "00" TO L-RET
    ELSE
        MOVE "23" TO L-RET
    END-IF.

DO-WRITE.
    MOVE L-DI-REC TO DI-REC
    WRITE DI-REC
    EVALUATE WS-FS
        WHEN "00" MOVE "00" TO L-RET
        WHEN "02" MOVE "00" TO L-RET
        WHEN "22" MOVE "22" TO L-RET
        WHEN OTHER MOVE "92" TO L-RET
    END-EVALUATE.

DO-DELETE.
    MOVE L-DI-DOC TO DI-DOC
    READ INTN-FILE
    IF WS-FS NOT = "00" AND WS-FS NOT = "02"
        MOVE "23" TO L-RET
    ELSE
        DELETE INTN-FILE
        IF WS-FS = "00"
            MOVE "00" TO L-RET
        ELSE
            MOVE "92" TO L-RET
        END-IF
    END-IF.
END PROGRAM "30INTNE0".
